▫️Choose Ubuntu 22.04, t2.micro

▫️Open Security Group → add inbound rule for port 5000 (TCP)

▫️connect to your EC2 (ssh)

▫️paste these commands : 

sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y
sudo apt install python3-pip -y
pip3 install flask joblib scikit-learn numpy

scp -i your-key.pem titanic_model.pkl app.py ubuntu@<ec2-ip>:/home/ubuntu/

